| brands     | [&quot;Brand A&quot;, &quot;Brand B&quot;]            |
| categories | [&quot;Category A&quot;, &quot;Category B&quot;]      |
| colors     | [&quot;Red&quot;, &quot;White&quot;, &quot;Blue&quot;, &quot;Green&quot;] |
